@NODE Support "Support - Contacting author and getting updates"

AUTHOR
  If you have some questions, comments or suggestions email me at:
  slme10k1@bologna.nettuno.it or vat0062@iperbole.bologna.it

  NOTE: Menu options are provided for writing to me.

  French and italian users may write in their own languages.

UPDATES

  Whenever a new version of NetMail gets released, i will announce them in
  comp.sys.amiga.announce newsgroup and via email to all registered users.
  The latest version of NetMail is available on Aminet FTP servers at:

  ftp://<aminetsite>/aminet/comm/mail/NetMail-<ver>.lha
@ENDNODE


@NODE ToDo "To do - Future enhancements"

Architecture evolution

  Actually NetMail is an evolutionary rapid prototype written entirely in Rexx.
  Starting with next release, portions of code in C will be added.
  Progressive C rewriting process will end with production of:

    - a server library with rexx interface that provides all mail services.

    - a GUI client that provides access to all program features.

    - other clients (with or without GUI) to provide embedded mail services to
      third party applications.
@ENDNODE


